        {
            "title": "油價高收1%或以上　本周累跌近4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際期油價格周五收市升1%或以上，全星期則下跌近4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094825_OilPrice_AP_source-ap_-2-1-1-1-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094825_OilPrice_AP_source-ap_-2-1-1-1-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報每桶67.04美元，升68美仙，升幅1% ; 倫敦布蘭特期油收市報每桶70.36美元，升90美仙，升幅近1.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">本周累計，紐約期油仍跌3.9%，連跌周數延伸至7周。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外電報道，美國特朗普要求俄羅斯總統普京同意停戰，否則將對俄羅斯原油實施更嚴厲制裁。其後，俄羅斯副總理諾瓦克稱，石油出口國組織及盟友(OPEC+)雖然同意4月增產，但也可能在最後一刻改變計劃，消息利好油價。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道稱，如果俄羅斯與烏克蘭停戰，美國將尋求讓俄羅斯原油更快地重返國際市場。此外，聯儲局主席鮑威爾重申不急於減息，油價高位回落。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14760994-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b61%e6%88%96%e4%bb%a5%e4%b8%8a%e3%80%80%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e7%b4%af%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%914",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-08 10:45:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "道指高收222點一周累跌逾2%  特斯拉本周挫逾一成六周連跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股3大指數反覆高收，聯儲局主席鮑伒爾表示經濟仍然良好，舒緩市場憂慮，美股先跌後升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240425_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240425_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國2月非農業新增職位15.1萬個少過預期，失業率升至4.1%，一度拖累大市向下；但聯儲局主席鮑威爾表示，要觀望總統特朗普關稅政策，再決定下一步利率行動，無需倉促減息，指數倒升收市。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數低開76點後，跌幅曾擴大至403點，低見42175點；其後最多倒升319點，高見42898，收市報42801點，升222點，升幅0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數最多曾跌0.95%，收市倒升0.7%，升126點，報18196點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標準普爾500指數報5770點，升31點，升幅近0.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數反彈0.47%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">本周累計，道指錄得2.4%跌幅；標指回落3.1%，為去年9月以來最差單周表現；納指本周下挫3.5%，金龍中國指數則回升4.9%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：沃爾瑪(Walmart)官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240821_FI_source-web_Walmart-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：沃爾瑪(Walmart)官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240821_FI_source-web_Walmart-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：沃爾瑪(Walmart)官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際商業機器(IBM)高收逾5%，沃爾瑪跌逾3%，分別是表現最好及最差的道指成份股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\"><strong>馬斯克任職DOGE後特斯拉每周股價均跌</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">特斯拉周五股價一度下瀉4.8%，收市僅跌0.3%，本周累計仍急降10.4%，較歷史最高位倒退約48%，去年11月美國大選以來的累計升幅蒸發；特朗普當選總統以來，特斯拉市值一度增加7000億美元，但行政總裁馬斯克充當特朗普政府效率部(DOGE)顧問角色以來，特斯拉股價連跌6周，即每周均錄得跌幅。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/Earns_Tesla_42500_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/Earns_Tesla_42500_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝達(NVIDIA)股價曾滑落2.7%，市值較史上最高位縮水1萬億美元，收市轉漲1.9%，本周累計仍瀉9.8%，此前兩周先後跌7.2%和2.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">波音跌2.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大型科技股個別發展，蘋果升近2%，但亞馬遜及微軟跌近1%。金融股下跌，摩根大通和高盛跌逾1%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240222_FI_source-ap__Nvidia-1_FB.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240222_FI_source-ap__Nvidia-1_FB.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14760977-%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6222%e9%bb%9e%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e7%b4%af%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be2-%e7%89%b9%e6%96%af%e6%8b%89%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be%e4%b8%80%e6%88%90%e5%85%ad%e5%91%a8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240801_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1-704.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-08 10:35:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "德股低收約1.8%本周升2%  奢侈品急挫",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲主要股市收市下跌。泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市回吐0.46%，報553點，早段一度滑落0.98%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-1-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-1-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：德國證交所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">受累美國關稅政策，市場憂慮奢侈品銷售表現受影響，相關股份受壓，歷峰集團(Richemont)股價急挫5.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數報23008點，跌410點，跌幅約1.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數報8120點，跌76點，跌幅0.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數報8679點，跌2點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報38592點，回落0.48%或186點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報13257點，反彈0.17%或22點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">全星期計，德股累計上升2%，法股升0.1%，英股跌近1.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14760979-%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e7%b4%841-8%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e5%8d%872-%e5%a5%a2%e4%be%88%e5%93%81%e6%80%a5%e6%8c%ab",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-08 10:20:51",
